title: Why MIS?
date: 2019-08-28
labels: MIS
---
I choose to add MIS as a second major because of professor Eduard Mercs class. He was one of my best teachers to this day. What he lectured on outside of the class material itself was very heavy on the internet of things and cybersecurity. These topics were extremely intriguing and seemed absolutely relevant. After recommending the major I could do nothing but take up the opportunity. 
